The input string `s` must not be null.
The input string `s` must consist of only the letters 'a', 'b', and 'c'.
The input integer `k` must be non-negative.
The length of the input string `s` must be between 1 and 10^5 (inclusive).
The value of `k` must be between 0 and the length of `s` (inclusive).
